        <item>
            <title>Version 0.5.0</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
<h2>What's New in 0.5.0</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Auto-update support</strong> — Memois now checks for updates automatically using Sparkle</li>
    <li><strong>Repair button</strong> — Recover recordings when chunks exist but the merged audio file is missing</li>
    <li><strong>Fix: recording file not found</strong> — Fixed race condition when stopping and immediately starting a new recording</li>
</ul>
            ]]></description>
